.PP
\fBParameters:\fP
.RS 4
\fIbased\fP widget which we'll split 
.br
\fIedge\fP at which edge «based» will be splitted 
.br
\fIpixels\fP how many pixels to split off 
.br
\fIcaption\fP initial image text
.RE
.PP
\fBReturns:\fP
.RS 4
pointer to the newly created image or NULL on error.
.RE
.PP

